{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Console.count()","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/count","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console_API\">Console API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console\"><code>Console</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/assert\"><code>assert()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/clear\"><code>clear()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/count\"><code>count()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/countReset\"><code>countReset()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/debug\"><code>debug()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/dir\"><code>dir()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/dirxml\"><code>dirxml()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/error\"><code>error()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/group\"><code>group()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/groupCollapsed\"><code>groupCollapsed()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/groupEnd\"><code>groupEnd()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/info\"><code>info()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/log\"><code>log()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/profile\"><code>profile()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/profileEnd\"><code>profileEnd()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/table\"><code>table()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/time\"><code>time()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/timeEnd\"><code>timeEnd()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/timeLog\"><code>timeLog()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/timeStamp\"><code>timeStamp()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/trace\"><code>trace()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/warn\"><code>warn()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Console API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/console\"><code>Window.console</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/console\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.console</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Exibe o número de vezes em que a chamada&nbsp;<code>count()</code>&nbsp;em particular foi invocada. Essa função recebe um argumento opcional&nbsp;<code>label</code>.</p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> This feature is available in <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a></p>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<p>Se&nbsp;<code>label</code> é fornecido, essa função exibe o número de vezes que a função <code>count()</code>&nbsp;foi chamada com a respectiva label.</p>\n\n<p>Se&nbsp;<code>label</code> for omitido, a função exibe o número de vezes que a função&nbsp;<code>count()&nbsp;</code>foi chamada na respectiva linha.</p>\n\n<p>Por exemplo, no código abaixo:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> usuario <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">cumprimentar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">count</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"olá \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> usuario<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nusario <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"bob\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">cumprimentar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nusario <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"alice\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">cumprimentar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">cumprimentar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">count</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>A saída do console será algo como:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">\"&lt;no label&gt;: 1\"\n\"&lt;no label&gt;: 2\"\n\"&lt;no label&gt;: 3\"\n\"&lt;no label&gt;: 1\"\n</pre>\n\n<p>Note a última linha da saída do console: a chamada individual de&nbsp;<code>count()</code>&nbsp;na linha 11 é tratada como um evento independente.</p>\n\n<p>Se passarmos a variável&nbsp;<code>usuario</code>&nbsp;como o argumento&nbsp;<code>label</code> para a primeira invocação de&nbsp;<code>count()</code>, e a string \"alice\" para a segunda:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> usuario <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">cumprimentar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">count</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>usuario<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"olá \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> usuario<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nusuario <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"bob\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">cumprimentar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nusuario <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"alice\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">cumprimentar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">cumprimentar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">count</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"alice\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Teremos uma saída assim:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">\"bob: 1\"\n\"alice: 1\"\n\"alice: 2\"\n\"alice: 3\"</pre>\n\n<p>Agora estamos mantendo contagens separadamente baseadas no valor de&nbsp;<code>label</code>. Como a label&nbsp;\"alice\" na linha 11 corresponde ao valor de&nbsp;<code>usuario</code>&nbsp;duas vezes, não é considerado um evento independente.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">console.count([label]);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parâmetros","title":"Parâmetros","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"label\"><code>label</code></dt>\n <dd>Uma string. Se for fornecida, exibe o número de vezes que &nbsp;<code>count()</code> foi invocada com a mesma label.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://console.spec.whatwg.org/#count\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Console API<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'console.count()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>Definição inicial</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n